transforms.code:
listDD = []
	#listDD.append({'value':'Sin Orden','label':'Sin Orden'})
	eqPath = value
	date = system.date.setTime(system.date.addDays(system.date.now(),-1),0,0,0)
	woName = "*"	
	woFilter = system.mes.workorder.createMESWorkOrderFilter()
	woFilter.setWorkOrderNameFilter(woName)
	woFilter.setClosedBeginDate(date)
	woFilter.setEquipmentPathFilter(eqPath)
	results = system.mes.workorder.getMESWorkOrders(woFilter)
	
	for result in results:
		temp = {'Siguiente:':result.getName()}
		listDD.append(temp)
	
	if len(listDD) == 0:
		listDD.append({'Siguiente:':'Sin Orden'})
	return listDD

config.script:
import java
	path = self.view.params.eqPath
	
	try:
		# Get next programmed Work Order
		pending = self.view.custom.pendingWoList
		workOrderName = str( pending[0]['Siguiente:'] ) 
		WO = system.mes.workOrder.getMESWorkOrder( workOrderName )
		materialName = WO.getPropertyValue('MaterialRef').split(', ')[1]
		
		#If this button is enabled, that means activeList.size = 0
		system.mes.oee.beginOEERun(workOrderName, materialName, path)
		self.parent.getChild("FlexContainer_1").getChild("Label_Msg").props.text = 'Orden '+workOrderName+' Iniciada'
	
	except java.lang.Exception, value:
		self.parent.getChild("FlexContainer_1").getChild("Label_Msg").props.text = str(value.getMessage())
		system.mes.oee.endOEEProduction(path)

transforms.code:
tagPath = str(self.view.custom.tagPath)+'From Time Stamp'
	startDate = self.view.custom.startDate
	endDate = value
	params = {'eqPath':self.view.params.eqPath}
	data = system.mes.analysis.executeAnalysis(startDate,endDate,'hora-hora',params).getDataset()
	pyData = system.dataset.toPyDataSet(data)
	dic = []
	for row in pyData:
		temp = {'Hour': row['Hour Interval'],'Target':row['Outfeed Standard Count'],'Production':row['OEE Outfeed Count']}
		dic.append(temp)
	return dic
